reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent Smart Touch Lamp!
reviews.reviewText: This is a great smart touch lamp! We have a Hatch for one of our kids and needed to get another nightlight that is easy for them, and us, to operate. We wanted to save so money so we went with this option and we are SO glad we did! I think we've decided that we prefer this over the name brand! It has many colors, a time, can be used from mine and my wife's phone, we can control the brightness (which is key to a good night light) and it is aesthetically pleasing. Would definitely recommend this lamp!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very cute light.
reviews.reviewText: This is a cute, easy to use lamp. Love that there are so many color options and that it syncs with my music. Very nice addition to my space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice little lamp with many options of modes and colors
reviews.reviewText: I like that you can use it via buttons on lamp or thru the phone app.The phone app gives you a lot of options of various modes and colors.In the app you can actually schedule the lamp to come on at a certain time then go off later at a certain time.It says you can use it inside or outside.I have not left it on that long at a time but it says it can last at least 8 hours or more at full brightness which is very reasonable.It is not super brilliant but does give off the expected amount of light for being a small lamp.Given all the features, even being able to schedule it to come on and go off at a specified time, I think it is a reasonable value.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Colorful Table Lamp, More for Kids.
reviews.reviewText: This table lamp is more for letting kids to go to bed in a fun and enjoyable way. The lamp is made with high quality plastic material, and the lamp has beautiful color. The app is easy to install and the blue tooth could easily be connected. You could log in without creating an account. I got it set up easily and from the app I could control and select and the color I like. All the selection and control could also be done on the lamp itself. I like that it is not very bright, and the light-source is all contained and diffused. Although technically an adult may not have much need for a colorful table lamp, I think kids will find it interesting and would like to touch and play with the color before going to bed. It could be a favorable gift. Would recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Disappointing to say the least
reviews.reviewText: This little lamp isn’t really all that bright it doesn’t play music but the light dances along to whatever you may be playing on your phone buuuuuut you can only import music from iTunes or a pc or music that’s already saved to your phone the microphone capabilities only allow for the lamp to change color while you speak into a mic on the app all in all just not what I was expecting at all more of a night light for a child than anything

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars well made and colorful
reviews.reviewText: this Smart Touch Bedside Table Lamp is well made with beautiful, variety of color settings. My kids go wild on it as they try to play and to explore with different color schemes. Love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Happy Accent Light
reviews.reviewText: This is a fun, versatile accent lamp. I like having small lamps such as these in my kitchen and my main living space. Layering types of lighting in a room adds to the overall ambiance and builds a sense of well being. This light design is very simple and would work with many interior styles. The user interface is fairly easy to set up and the color choices endless. I keep mine in the dimmer, more golden range as I am looking for a vibe rather than actual room brightening. There are quite a few choices in this category, but I feel that this lamps gets the details right, making it a good choice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Powerful adjustable table lamp
reviews.reviewText: This is an attractive light which lets you adjust color, color temperature and brightness by different touches of the top button. Thus, it is good for reading in bed, but just as good as a night light. It has features which lets you have it change lighting to the sound of music via an internal microphone but this is not a feature that I cared to even try. It might be kind of fun for kids for a party. I did have a question about one of the features and was able to contact technical support from within the included app, and within 24 hours got a good answer to my questions.
